name: SAI TARA TRUST
briefDescription: Sai Tara Trust pleased to evaluate the aims/projects of the trust for the well-being of the society. Since last five years, our trust has been working for Children’s welfare and education. We want children to gain interest in studies, so our trust organizes an award function to felicitate the children by providing books and encourage them for study.Sai Tara Trust pleased to evaluate the aims/projects of the trust for the well-being of the society.
